        <speech by="#1ba97dc9-c731-4cb3-ae68-515251dcee0b">
          <from>HON. RAMONA JENNEX</from>
          <p>HON. RAMONA JENNEX : Before I bring forth my resolution may I have permission for an introduction.</p>
